quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  30,51,aur agar hum aisi howa bhejen ke woh ( is ke sabab ) khaiti ko dekhen ( ke ) zard ( ho gayi hai ) to is ke baad woh nashukri karne lag jayen
  30,52,to tum mardon ki ( baat ) nahi suna satke aur nah behroon ko jab woh peeth phair kar phir jayen aawaz suna satke ho
  30,53,aur nah andhon ko unn ki gumraahi se ( nikaal kar ) raah raast par laskte ho. tum to unhi logon ko suna satke ho jo hamari aayton par imaan laatay hain so wohi farmanbardar hain
  30,54,khuda hi to hai jis ne tum ko ( ibtida mein ) kamzor haalat mein pedakiya phir kamzoree ke baad taaqat inayat ki phir taaqat ke baad kamzoree aur burhapa diya. woh jo chahta hai peda karta hai aur woh sahib Danish aur sahib qudrat hai
  30,55,aur jis roz qayamat barpaa hogi gunehgaar kasmain khayen ge ke woh ( duniya mein ) aik gharri se ziyada nahi rahay they. isi terhan woh ( raste se ) ultay jatay they
  30,56,aur jin logon ko ilm aur imaan diya gaya tha woh kahin ge ke khuda ki kitaab ke mutabiq tum qayamat taq rahay ho. aur yeh qayamat hi ka din hai lekin tum ko is ka yaqeen hi nahi tha
  30,57,to is roz zalim logon ko un ka izr kuch faida nah day ga aur nah unn se tauba qubool ki jaye gi
  30,58,aur hum ne logon ke ( samjhane ke ) liye is quran mein har terhan ki misaal bayan kar di hai aur agar tum unn ke samnay koi nishani paish karo to yeh kafir keh den ge ke tum to jhutay ho
  30,59,isi terhan khuda unn logon ke dilon par jo samajh nahi rakhtay mohar laga deta hai
  30,60,pas tum sabr karo bay shak khuda ka wada sacha hai aur ( dekho ) jo log yaqeen nahi rakhtay woh tumhe oocha nah bnadin
